Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計將兩三日之內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在靛藍花園登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 上次買的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它身上集結了瓦洛夫家的精華技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的名字是 瓦洛夫R7！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴邊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 就妳一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被兩個人抓走了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…菲莉雅她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定他們還在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去救她！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好呀 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 飯一口也沒吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳以後就要一直跟著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 張開妳的小嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 你在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想再見到那個臭小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把我弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓妳再看到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在呼喚我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅的項鍊在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在東邊哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瑪也抓到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快交給政府吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當初倒是這麼約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們什麼時候碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府來回收利瑪的部隊似乎已經上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以為政府諮詢會的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們第八軍特務師團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有著共同目標的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們對此沒有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼您準備如何解釋最近自作主張的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的話還真是句句帶刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們發現各位在未事前協商的情況下就開展了作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而為何執行任務的是我屬下的士官…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你指的是斯圖爾特大尉 那是他個人的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只願被認作禁忌的利瑪之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帶給這顆星球帶來新的繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與更偉大的興盛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面是茜素廢礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反應就在這裡面哞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼只能進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪晃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認過碰面地點了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事早辦妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動不動就干涉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再說一句？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8點鐘方向有熱源反應接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是政府的運輸器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,識別代碼是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放大畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在裡面哞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞…哞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別躲來躲去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼哞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發動我的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿你缺胳膊當藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這點實力…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想滿足…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別他媽夾著尾巴逃了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜 我只有一把傘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你自己用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
